data.title: Western Harbour Tunnel
data.meta_description: Western Harbour Tunnel infrastructure project Sydney Harbour ACCIONA's Infrastructure Business in Australia is construction in collaboration with Transport for New South Wales.
data.text:
Stage 2 includes connections from Stage 1 at Cove Street, Birchgrove, to the Warringah Freeway near North Sydney, tunnelling under Sydney Harbour and the complete tunnel fit-out.

Transport for NSW awarded the Western Harbour Tunnel Stage 2 contract to ACCIONA in December 2022.
